    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "Im pursuing Electronics and Telecommunications Engineering at this college, and I must say the teaching staff is very good and well-experienced.",
        "There are many companies like TCS, Wipro, etc., that offer internships, and the roles can be programmer, debugger, etc.",
        "Companies that visited our colleges in the year 2021 were Infosys, Zesar, Tudip, Zensoft Services, and many more.",
        "The college also gives scholarships to bright students on its level to help them in completing their education.",
        "The campus was amazing, and the best thing is its environment, which helped in learning.",
        "The college has its own on-campus hostel with comfortable rooms for three people. Each room has an attached bathroom. The college also has two messes on campus.",
        "Our college has a very excellent campus, including a big sports playground, canteen, and hostel with better quality drinking water."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        "This college is a private college. Only government colleges require compulsory internships. Those colleges that depend on the university will resume internships. Only a few students are placed in the campus drive.",
